flowchart LR
    Author([Author])
    Reader([Reader])
    PostSvc[Post Service]
    Posts[(Posts DB<br/>partition by author)]
    FanOut[Fan-out Service<br/>push if < 10k followers]
    Timeline[(Timeline Cache<br/>sorted set per user)]
    FeedSvc[Feed Service<br/>merge + ML rank]
    Media[(Media + CDN)]

    Author -->|new post| PostSvc
    PostSvc -->|persist| Posts
    PostSvc --> FanOut
    FanOut -->|push to followers| Timeline
    FanOut -.->|celebrity: skip push| Posts

    Reader -->|load feed| FeedSvc
    FeedSvc -->|pre-built list| Timeline
    FeedSvc -->|pull celebrity posts| Posts
    FeedSvc -->|hydrate media| Media
    FeedSvc -->|ranked feed| Reader

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Author,Reader external
    class PostSvc,FanOut,FeedSvc service
    class Posts,Timeline,Media store
